sheep camp
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number: 1
Definition:a specific area within paddocks where sheep congregate naturally [particularly on hills in  evenings.]
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
